<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>A Florida home used in the 1990 film Edward Scissorhands has sold for a fraction above asking price.</p>

<p>The house in the Tampa Bay area town of Lutz was purchased for $230,000 last week by 'a family of Edward Scissorhands fans' according to TMZ.</p>

<p>The sum represented a $6000 increase on the initial asking price of $224,000. </p>

<p>Open house: A Florida home used in the 1990 film Edward Scissorhands has sold for a fraction above asking price. Dianne Wiest and Johnny Depp seen here in the film</p>

<p>One of the buyers grew up in the area, according to TMZ, and had even witnessed the cult classic being filmed in his area as a child.</p>

<p>The house -that was used for the interior and exterior shots for the Boggs family- received 'about a dozen offers' in its first week on the market, according to the gossip site.  </p>

<p>The Tim Burton directed fantasy romance movie starring Johnny Depp and Winona Ryder was filmed in the town of Lutz in the Tampa Bay area of Florida in 1989. </p>

<p>The 1,432 square home, featuring three bedrooms and two bathrooms, was listed for $224,000, according to the Tampa Bay Times. </p>

<p>Sold: The Tim Burton directed fantasy romance movie Edward Scissorhands starring Johnny Depp and Winona Ryder was filmed in the town of Lutz in the Tampa Bay area of Florida in 1989. And 31 years after filming wrapped, the home that was used for the interior and exterior shots for the Boggs family is on the market</p>

<p>The home is located in a subdivision called Carpenters Run in the town of Lutz in the Tampa Bay area, listed by Stacie Savoy of Berkshire Hathaway Florida Properties Group.</p>

<p>The corner lot home served as the home for the Boggs family, and where Edward Scissorhands, played by Johnny Depp stays as a house guest.</p>

<p>It starred Winona Ryder as Edward's love interest Kim Boggs, as well as Dianne Wiest Anthony Michael Hall, Kathy Baker, Vincent Price and Alan Arkin; The movie Edward Scissorhands hit theaters on December 6, 1990. </p>

<p>It began filming at the home just months after it was built. </p>

